highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Ahmedabad. “Kesariya” is the highest at #1.
“Shree Hanuman Chalisa” by Hariharan is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Ahmedabad, up 32 spots at #55.
“Raataan Lambiyan (From "Shershaah")” by Tanishk Bagchi, Jubin Nautiyal, and Asees Kaur has been on Top Songs Ahmedabad the longest, at 52 weeks straight.
“Saiyyan” by Kailash Kher, Paresh Kamath, and Naresh Kamath is the highest new entry on Top Songs Ahmedabad at #93.
